Welcome to our Nova Platform repository.

We are attempting to put the innovation process  on the cloud with this Open Innovation Platform and help turn ideas into successful products.

The core technology stack behind Nova Platform's framework is node.js + expressjs + mongodb

We will furnish you with more details here as time goes by.

